section.visitor-toggle.container-fluid.text-center
  h1.ih-header.text-center
    | Why did we build InHouse?
  .ih-sm-divider
  p
    | At InHouse we want to help you make strong and loyal relationships with your clients and business partners.
  p
    em Who are you?
  .btn-group
    a(ng-class="{'active' : !lenderOnly}", ng-click='lenderOnly = false') Agent
    a(ng-class="{'active' : lenderOnly}", ng-click='lenderOnly = true') Lender
  .down.text-center.text-muted.text-uppercase
    small.block scroll down
    i.fa.fa-angle-down
section#scrollhook.page-content.container-fluid
  .row.agent-only(ng-show='!lenderOnly')
    .container
      .row.agent-only
        h1.ih-header.text-center How it works
        .ih-sm-divider
        .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-12.card
          .text-center
            img(src='ua/images/connect-agent.svg', alt='Connect Icon')
          h2.text-center.fc-03 Connect
          .ih-md-divider
          p
            | Integrate your MLS. InHouse pulls listings data and photographs directly from your MLS so you never have to re-upload listing information again.
        .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-12.card
          .text-center
            img(src='ua/images/design-agent.svg', alt='Design Icon')
          h2.text-center.fc-03 Design
          .ih-md-divider
          p
            | Customize your brand style. Our beautiful designs ensure that your brand looks consistent and polished everywhere.
        .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-12.card
          .text-center
            img(src='ua/images/relax-agent.svg', alt='Relax Icon')
          h2.text-center.fc-03 Relax
          .ih-md-divider
          p
            | Sit back and let us do the work. InHouse will have all listing promo materials ready in your inbox automatically for every new and sold listing.
        .btn-row.text-center
          a.btn.btn-primary(href='#/signup') sign-up today
      .row.agent-only
        h1.ih-header.text-center What you get
        .ih-sm-divider
        .container-fluid.agent-how
          .row
            .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
              img.img-responsive.hidden-lg.hidden-md.hidden-sm(src='ua/images/listing-sites.svg')
              h2.fc-03 Listing Landing Pages
              h5 Tell a home's story with a beautiful website.
              p
                | Instantly launch and host interactive, mobile-optimized listing websites that provide your clients with all the information they need about a home and surrounding area.
              p
                em
                  small *Only available with Lender Partner
              a.btn.btn-default.hidden(href='https://listing.getinhouse.io', target='_blank', rel='noopener') view example
            .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.text-center
              img.img-responsive.hidden-xs(src='ua/images/listing-sites.svg')
          .row
            .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.text-center
              img.img-responsive(src='ua/images/listing-socialmedia.svg')
            .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.text-right
              h2.fc-03 Social Media Posts & Ads
              h5 Reach beyond your friends and followers.
              p
                | Launch 2, 5, or 10 day ad campaigns for your new listings and open houses with beautiful branded ads and posts. Drive leads back to your listing pages or website.
              p
                em
                  small *Only available with Lender Partner
              a.btn.btn-default.hidden(href='ua/samples/inhouse-socialmedia.pdf', target='_blank', rel='noopener') view example
          .row
            .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
              img.hidden-lg.hidden-md.hidden-sm.img-responsive(src='ua/images/listing-print.svg')
              h2.fc-03 Listing Presentations & Flyers
              h5 The easiest way to make stunning real estate flyers. Period.
              p
                | Create beautiful, branded listing and open house flyers and listing presentations in minutes. Print them right at your office or send them straight to your preferred print shop.
              a.btn.btn-default.hidden(href='ua/samples/inhouse-print.pdf', target='_blank', rel='noopener') view example
            .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.text-center
              img.img-responsive.hidden-xs(src='ua/images/listing-print.svg')
    section.pricing.bkc-03.fw
      .container.text-center.agent-only
        h1.ih-lg-header agents start free
        a.btn.btn-default(href='#/signup') sign-up today
  .row(ng-show='lenderOnly')
    .container
      // show for lenders only
      .row.lender-only
        h1.ih-header.text-center How it works
        .ih-sm-divider
        .col-lg-4.col-md-4.col-sm-4.col-xs-12.card
          .text-center
            img(src='ua/images/connect-lender.svg', alt='Connect Icon')
          h2.text-center.fc-03 Connect
          .ih-md-divider
