      .row.lender-only
        h1.ih-header.text-center What you get
        .ih-sm-divider
        .container-fluid.lender-how
          .row
            .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
              img.img-responsive.hidden-lg.hidden-md.hidden-sm(src='ua/images/lender-agents.svg')
              h2.fc-03
                | Manage all your agent relationships
                br
                | from one easy-to-use dashboard
              ul.bullets
                li
                  i.fa.fa-caret-right.text-muted
                  |  Invite as many agents as you'd like, whenever, wherever
                li
                  i.fa.fa-caret-right.text-muted
                  |  Keep track of leads generated per agent
                li
                  i.fa.fa-caret-right.text-muted
                  |  Receive email notifications for your partners' new and sold listings
            .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.text-center
              img.img-responsive.hidden-xs(src='ua/images/lender-agents.svg')
          .row
            .col-lg-6.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-12.text-center
              img.img-responsive(src='ua/images/lender-listings.svg')
